INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
1) install nodejs (brew install nodejs on osx)
2) install ruby (needed for compass utility, not for deployment)
3) gem install bundler
4) bundle
5) npm install
6) bower install

TO BUILD FOR DEPLOYMENT
1) grunt build
2) deployable app will be in dist dir

TO RUN TESTS
1) grunt test:unit
2) grunt test:e2e

TO DEVELOP
1) grunt serve
2) open browser to http://localhost:9000
3) edit files in app/ and test/ dirs
4) web app is automatically reloaded when files are saved
